SUMMARY:Hot Ones Challenge: Singing for Summer Salaries
DESCRIPTION:Come watch Professor McFadden (https://law.indiana.edu/about/
 people/details?name=mcfadden-lane)\, Professor Fuentes-Rohwer (https://la
 w.indiana.edu/about/people/details?name=fuentes-rohwer-luis)\, and Jack P
 hillips (JD '26) participate in a Hot Ones style challenge to raise money
  for Singing for Summer Salaries! Participants will answer a series of tr
 ivia questions. For every incorrect answer\, they must eat a hot wing wit
 h an increasing heat level. Dean Ochoa (https://law.indiana.edu/about/peo
 ple/details?name=ochoa-christiana) will moderate. Faculty and staff are e
 ncouraged to attend.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Come watch Professor <a href="https://l
 aw.indiana.edu/about/people/details?name=mcfadden-lane">McFadden</a>\, Pr
 ofessor <a href="https://law.indiana.edu/about/people/details?name=fuente
 s-rohwer-luis">Fuentes-Rohwer</a>\, and Jack Phillips (JD '26) participat
 e in a Hot Ones style challenge to raise money for Singing for Summer Sal
 aries! Participants will answer a series of trivia questions. For every i
 ncorrect answer\, they must eat a hot wing with an increasing heat level.
  <a href="https://law.indiana.edu/about/people/details?name=ochoa-christi
 ana">Dean Ochoa</a> will moderate. Faculty and staff are encouraged to at
 tend.&#160\;</p>
