X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE-CAPTION:Emily Bazelon is a Senior Research Scholar in L
 aw at Yale Law School. She is also a <a class="ext" title="(opens in a ne
 w window)" href="https://www.nytimes.com/by/emily-bazelon" target="_blank
 " rel="noopener noreferrer" data-extlink="" data-once="printLink">staff w
 riter</a> at the <em>New York Times Magazine</em> and author of two natio
 nal bestsellers. She has been a Soros media fellow\, an editor and writer
  at <em>Legal Affairs</em> magazine\, and a law clerk on the U.S. Court o
 f Appeals for the First Circuit. Bazelon is a graduate of Yale College an
 d Yale Law School.
