LOCATION:LOWELL E. BAIER HALL/IU MAURER SCHOOL OF LAW - Room Number: DeLa
 ney Moot Court Room (123)
GEO:39.165074;-86.526424
SUMMARY:Sherman Minton Moot Court Competition Finals
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the final round of the annual Sherman Minton Moot
  Court Competition.Case InformationJACOB LAWRIN\, in his individual capac
 ity as Chief Administrator and Commanding Officer of the Nuclear Bomb Loc
 ation and Security Team for the United States Department of Energy\, Defe
 ndant-Appellant v. MIKEY VALDEZ\, individually and on behalfof all simila
 rly situated plaintiffs.  The case involves residents of an off-the-grid 
 intentional community who were evicted and relocated by a federal governm
 ent agency that\, in an emergency situation\, used the community as a bas
 e of operations and sleeping quarters. The plaintiffs allege that their T
 hird Amendment rights were violated\, and that they should be able to bri
 ng the case as a class-action lawsuit.  &#160\;A reception with hors d'oe
 uvres will follow the competition.https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/dow-
 robert-michael-jr (https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/dow-robert-michael-
 jr)https://www.in.gov/courts/supreme/justices/derek-molter/ (https://www.
 in.gov/courts/supreme/justices/derek-molter/)https://www.insd.uscourts.go
 v/content/magistrate-judge-m-kendra-klump (https://www.insd.uscourts.gov/
 content/magistrate-judge-m-kendra-klump)  Please RSVP to attend in person
 .  This event may also be viewed live on the IU Maurer YouTube Channel (h
 ttps://nam12.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yout
 ube.com%2Fc%2FIUMaurer&amp\;data=05%7C02%7Ccwbrowni%40iu.edu%7C7eeab43573
 9d4f38596608de601c523a%7C1113be34aed14d00ab4bcdd02510be91%7C1%7C0%7C63905
 3871915141567%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjA
 uMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&am
 p\;sdata=If2OX8WsH0s5Ic%2BFWBBc62HCo7HQI8GaPn7fzFflGJE%3D&amp\;reserved=0
 ). Registration is not required to view the livestream.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join us for the final round of the annu
 al Sherman Minton Moot Court Competition.</p><p><strong><span style="text
 -decoration: underline\;">Case Information</span></strong></p><p><em>JACO
 B LAWRIN\, in his individual capacity as Chief Administrator and Commandi
 ng Officer of the Nuclear Bomb Location and Security Team for the United 
 States Department of Energy\, Defendant-Appellant v. MIKEY VALDEZ\, indiv
 idually and on behalf</em><em>of all similarly situated plaintiffs.</em><
 /p><p>  The case involves residents of an off-the-grid intentional commun
 ity who were evicted and relocated by a federal government agency that\, 
 in an emergency situation\, used the community as a base of operations an
 d sleeping quarters. The plaintiffs allege that their Third Amendment rig
 hts were violated\, and that they should be able to bring the case as a c
 lass-action lawsuit.</p><p>  &#160\;A reception with hors d'oeuvres will 
 follow the competition.</p><p><a href="https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges
 /dow-robert-michael-jr">https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/dow-robert-mic
 hael-jr</a></p><p><a href="https://www.in.gov/courts/supreme/justices/der
 ek-molter/">https://www.in.gov/courts/supreme/justices/derek-molter/</a><
 /p><p><a href="https://www.insd.uscourts.gov/content/magistrate-judge-m-k
 endra-klump">https://www.insd.uscourts.gov/content/magistrate-judge-m-ken
 dra-klump</a></p><p>  Please RSVP to attend in person.</p><p>  This event
  may also be viewed live on the <a href="https://nam12.safelinks.protecti
 on.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FIUMaurer&amp\;dat
 a=05%7C02%7Ccwbrowni%40iu.edu%7C7eeab435739d4f38596608de601c523a%7C1113be
 34aed14d00ab4bcdd02510be91%7C1%7C0%7C639053871915141567%7CUnknown%7CTWFpb
 GZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIj
 oiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp\;sdata=If2OX8WsH0s5Ic%2BFWBBc
 62HCo7HQI8GaPn7fzFflGJE%3D&amp\;reserved=0">IU Maurer YouTube Channel</a>
 . Registration is not required to view the livestream.</p>
