SUMMARY:X-Act Transactional Law Team Demo with BLS
DESCRIPTION:Contract negotiations put the "action" in transactional law. 
 The BLS\, Prof's Need and Pogue\, and the X-Act transactional law team in
 vite students\, faculty\, and attorneys to an interactive\, condensed tra
 nsactional negotiation competition—60 heart-pounding minutes of positio
 ning\, asymmetric thinking\, and collaboration. This can't-miss event off
 ers a glimpse of the format for the upcoming Internal Transactional Compe
 tition in the fall of 2026\, and showcases Maurer's innovative curriculum
  and talent in the fastest growing sector of the legal field. &#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Contract negotiations put the "action" 
 in transactional law. The BLS\, Prof's Need and Pogue\, and the X-Act tra
 nsactional law team invite students\, faculty\, and attorneys to an inter
 active\, condensed transactional negotiation competition—60 heart-pound
 ing minutes of positioning\, asymmetric thinking\, and collaboration. Thi
 s can't-miss event offers a glimpse of the format for the upcoming Intern
 al Transactional Competition in the fall of 2026\, and showcases Maurer's
  innovative curriculum and talent in the fastest growing sector of the le
 gal field. &#160\;</p>
