DESCRIPTION:This is event is for all rising 2Ls and 3Ls interested in com
 peting in an external (intermural) moot court competition during the 2026
 -2027 school year. Professor McFadden will explain what some of those com
 petitions are\, what they require\, and how to apply. This event is NOT a
 bout the 2L Sherman Minton Moot Court Competition\, for which there is a 
 separate information session on March 31.  Most competitions require that
  competitors be enrolled in a full-time JD program. 3L students with Sher
 man Minton or other moot court experience will be preferred when selectin
 g teams\, but each year we do send highly competitive 2Ls to national com
 petitions\, so all interested students are encouraged to attend. Applicat
 ions for all 2026-2027 teams will be due by April 17.&#160\;
